  "text": "To examine GFP expression in postnatal bone marrow HSCs, we examined Sca-1 + Lineage À c-kit + CD48 À cells from the bone marrow of 2-, 4-, and 8 week-old mice. These cells represented 0.019% ± 0 .004% of bone marrow cells at 2 weeks but fell to 0.004% ± 0.0004% of bone marrow cells by 8 weeks of age. This population contains all of the detectable HSC activity in adult bone marrow and is highly enriched for HSCs [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . While 86% ± 5% of bone marrow Sca-1 + Line-",
